fields.name: INCO (International Nature Conservation Organization)
fields.description: This is a collaborative effort from authorities of Nature Sanctuaries such as the Gir Forest in India to protect and conserve nature and its inhabitants including endangered animals. Please UP our charity!

fields.name: ISO (International Sanitation Organization)
fields.description: This is a charity focused on providing clean water to area around the world struggling with clean water - a basic human resource. Lets put an END to World Thirst!

fields.name: A Home For Those In Need
fields.description: Help those who need a shelter by UP-ing our page and providing funds for those who need a home!
